data.description:
Up the Creek Farms is an event venue set on 8 beautiful acres, offering a charming and unique taste of old Florida.  Majestic oaks draped in Spanish moss, a pristine creek running the length of the property, and the historic Decklan house present a truly unique setting for any occasion.  The 6,000 square foot Boathouse completes the picture with its rustic, open-air feel and spectacular views of the property.  Rustic, but providing all the modern amenities: air, catering kitchen, beautifully appointed bathrooms. At Up the Creek Farms, we provide excellent personal service and attention to detail to create your one of a kind event.

Corporate & Private Events
- Board Meetings
- Networking Events
- Banquets and Lectures
- Business Development Meetings
- Photo Shoots 
- Community/Fundraisers
- Christmas & Holiday Parties
- Anniversaries & Family Reunions  

Weddings
Celebrate your special day in elegance and style at Up the Creek Farms. Wedding packages include private on-site parking, exclusive use of grounds, choice of outdoor ceremony location, and Boathouse reception for 150 guests. A private dressing room is available for the bride prior to the ceremony. We offer a variety of packages including an exclusive weekend package with accommodations at our Bed & Breakfast and optional rentals and services allowing you to create the wedding of your dreams.  Excellent photo opportunities and all the little details at Up the Creek Farms make for a very special day.   

Rehearsal, Baby & Bridal Showers
For smaller events, you may consider the Decklan House's historic and charming setting. Enjoy the historic home and share with your closest friends and family for a rehearsal dinner, baby or bridal shower. Included in use are the main living areas, wrap around porches, and pool deck.
